#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; tracks time spent on various tasks. It is useful for tracking "
"billable hours and can report the hours logged by task and day."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; spremlja čas, porabljen za različna opravila. Uporaben je za "
"sledenje plačljivim uram in lahko poroča o zabeleženih urah glede na "
"opravilo in dan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This time history can be exported to a comma-delimited text file for import "
"into other billing and/or project management tools."
msgstr ""
"To časovno zgodovino je mogoče izvoziti v besedilno datoteko, ločeno z "
"vejicami, za uvoz v druga orodja za obračunavanje in/ali upravljanje "
"projektov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; detects when your keyboard and mouse are idle and can "
"associate different tasks with different desktops, two tools that can help "
"keep the timer running on the correct task."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; zazna, kdaj sta tipkovnica in miška nedejavni in lahko poveže "
"različna opravila z različnimi namizji, dve orodji, ki lahko pomagata, da "
"časovnik deluje pri pravilnem opravilu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; was originally written by &Sirtaj.Singh.Kang;. Its home page "
"is <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/KTimeTracker\">https://userbase.kde."
"org/KTimeTracker</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; je prvotno napisal &Sirtaj.Singh.Kang;. Njegova domača stran "
"je <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/KTimeTracker\">https://userbase.kde."
"org/KTimeTracker</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &ktimetracker;"
msgstr "Uporaba &ktimetracker;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &ktimetracker;"
msgstr "Zagon &ktimetracker;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <command>ktimetracker</command> at a command prompt or select "
"<guimenuitem>Personal Time Tracker</guimenuitem> from the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Applications</guimenu><guisubmenu>Utilities</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> group in the <guimenu>Plasma Application Launcher</guimenu>. The "
"generic &Qt; and &kf5-full; command options are available, see man pages "
"qt5options and kf5options."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <command>ktimetracker</command> v ukazni poziv ali izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Osebni sledilnik časa</guimenuitem> v <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Aplikacije</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pripomočki</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> skupino v <guimenu>Zaganjalnik aplikacij Plasma</guimenu>. "
"Generični &Qt; in &kf5-full; na voljo so ukazne možnosti, glejte priročnik "
"strani qt5options in kf5options."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; provides an additional command option that allows you to "
"enter the name of the iCalendar file that is used to store your labor "
"history. You enter a remote iCalendar file by using &HTTP; or &FTP; as part "
"of the file name; for example, https://www.mysite.com/mydata/mylabor.ics."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; ponuja dodatno ukazno možnost, ki vam omogoča vnos imena "
"datoteke iCalendar, ki se uporablja za shranjevanje vaše zgodovine dela. "
"Oddaljeno datoteko iCalendar vnesete z &HTTP; ali &FTP; kot del imena "
"datoteke; na primer https://www.mysite.com/mydata/mylabor.ics."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks"
msgstr "Opravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You are a freelance software consultant with "
"many clients. Some clients have multiple projects. During the course of a "
"day, you switch back and forth between different projects. You need to track "
"your time to generate monthly invoices."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Ste samostojni svetovalec za programsko opremo "
"s številnimi strankami. Nekatere stranke imajo več projektov. Tekom dneva "
"preklapljate med različnimi projekti. Za ustvarjanje mesečnih računov morate "
"spremljati svoj čas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> Create one top-level task for each client and "
"a subtask for each client project. For projects that require more detailed "
"tracking, create a list of project subtasks. Track time by double-clicking "
"on the task you are currently working on."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Ustvarite eno opravilo najvišje ravni za vsako "
"stranko in podopravilo za vsak projekt stranke. Za projekte, ki zahtevajo "
"podrobnejše sledenje, ustvarite seznam projektnih podopravil. Sledite času "
"tako, da dvokliknete opravilo, ki ga trenutno opravljate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; provides great flexibility in tracking your time, allowing "
"unlimited tasks and task depth. Time may be logged to any task, and more "
"than one task can be active at any given time."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; zagotavlja veliko prilagodljivost pri sledenju vašemu času, "
"kar omogoča neomejene naloge in globino nalog. Čas se lahko zabeleži za "
"katero koli opravilo in v danem trenutku je lahko aktivnih več kot eno "
"opravilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; allows you to edit your task's history and to put a comment "
"for every event that you have stopped."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; omogoča urejanje zgodovine vašega opravila in dodajanje "
"komentarja za vsak dogodek, ki ste ga ustavili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a top-level task, select <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Task</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Task...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. To create a "
"subtask, highlight the parent task and select <menuchoice> <shortcut> "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Task</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Subtask...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti opravilo na najvišji ravni, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Naloga</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo opravilo...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Če želite ustvariti podopravilo, označite "
"nadrejeno opravilo in izberite <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Task</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo podopravilo...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &ktimetracker; exits, the task list is saved to a file on your disk. "
"When it next opens, it reloads the task list from the same file."
msgstr ""
"Ko &ktimetracker; zapusti, se seznam opravil shrani v datoteko na vašem "
"disku. Ko se naslednjič odpre, znova naloži seznam opravil iz iste datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; can import and export tasks to minimize your work. See <xref "
"linkend=\"interfaces\"/>."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; lahko uvozi in izvozi naloge, da zmanjša vaše delo. Glejte "
"<xref linkend=\"interfaces\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Timers"
msgstr "Časovniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> To remain solvent, you must bill an average of "
"five hours a day. To stay on track, you watch your daily and weekly totals."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Če želite ostati plačilno sposobni, morate "
"zaračunavati povprečno po pet ur na dan. Če želite ostati, opazujte svoje "
"dnevne in tedenske skupne vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> Reset the session timer at the beginning of "
"each work day and reset all timers at the beginning of each week."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Ponastavite časovnik seje na začetku vsakega "
"delovnega dne in ponastavite vse časovnike na začetku vsakega tedna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; makes tracking time simple. To start logging time against a "
"task, double-click on the task. To stop logging time, double-click the task "
"again. Active tasks display a small clock in the <guilabel>Session Time</"
"guilabel> column."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; omogoča enostavno sledenje času. Če želite začeti beležiti "
"čas za opravilo, dvokliknite opravilo. Če želite ustaviti beleženje časa, "
"znova dvokliknite opravilo. Aktivna opravila prikazujejo majhno uro v "
"stolpcu <guilabel>Čas seje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another visual clue of logging activity is the &ktimetracker; system tray "
"icon. When a task is active, the second hand in the icon moves. If you rest "
"the mouse pointer over this icon, the name of the active task will display "
"in a tooltip. If more than one task is active, the task names in the tooltip "
"are separated by commas."
msgstr ""
"Drug vizualni namig o dejavnosti beleženja je &ktimetracker; ikona sistemske "
"vrstice. Ko je opravilo aktivno, se sekundni kazalec v ikoni premakne. Če "
"miškin kazalec postavite nad to ikono, se bo v opisu orodja prikazalo ime "
"aktivnega opravila. Če je aktivnih več kot eno opravilo, so imena opravil v "
"opisu orodja ločena z vejicami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; maintains two timers for each task: one for the session time "
"and one for the total time. In the default configuration, &ktimetracker; "
"displays two columns for each timer, resulting in a total of four columns "
"for each task:"
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; vzdržuje dva časovnika za vsako opravilo: enega za čas seje "
"in enega za skupni čas. V privzeti konfiguraciji &ktimetracker; prikaže dva "
"stolpca za vsak časovnik, kar pomeni skupno štiri stolpce za vsako opravilo:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:190 index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Session Time"
msgstr "Čas seje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191 index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "The time spent on the task since the session began."
msgstr "Čas, porabljen za opravilo od začetka seje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:194 index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Čas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194 index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "The time spent on the task since all times were reset."
msgstr "Čas, porabljen za opravilo od ponastavitve vseh časov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:198 index.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total Session Time"
msgstr "Skupni čas seje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199 index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time spent on the task and all its subtasks since the session began."
msgstr "Čas, porabljen za opravilo in vse njegove podnaloge od začetka seje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:202 index.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total Time"
msgstr "Skupni čas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203 index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time spent on the task and all its subtasks since all times were reset."
msgstr ""
"Čas, porabljen za opravilo in vse njegove podopravila, odkar so bili vsi "
"časi ponastavljeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start a new session, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Start New Session</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Za začetek nove seje izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Začni novo sejo</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reset all times, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Reset All Times</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ponastaviti vse čase, izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponastavi vse čase</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Desktop Tracking"
msgstr "Sledenje namizju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You have two main projects that you switch "
"between each day. To help organize your work, you keep your project 1 files "
"on Desktop 1 and your project 2 files on Desktop 2."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Imate dva glavna projekta, med katerima vsak "
"dan preklapljate. Za lažje organiziranje dela hranite datoteke projekta 1 na "
"namizju 1 in datoteke projekta 2 na namizju 2."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> Associate project 1 task with Desktop 1 and "
"the project 2 task with Desktop 2. When you switch from Desktop 2 to Desktop "
"1 active, &ktimetracker; automatically stops the project 2 task and starts "
"the project 1 task."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Povežite opravilo projekta 1 z namizjem 1 in "
"opravilo projekta 2 z namizjem 2. Ko preklopite iz namizja 2 na namizje 1, "
"&ktimetracker; samodejno ustavi nalogo projekta 2 in zažene nalogo projekta "
"1."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To associate a task with one or more desktops, select <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Task</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Turn on <guilabel>Auto Tracking</guilabel> and select the "
"desktop or desktops to associate with this task. When any of the selected "
"desktops becomes active, after a short delay &ktimetracker; will be "
"automatically start logging time against that task."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nalogo povezati z enim ali več namizji, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Opravilo</guimenu > <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>. Vklopite <guilabel>Samodejno sledenje</guilabel> in izberite "
"namizje ali namizja, ki jih želite povezati s to nalogo. Ko postane katero "
"od izbranih namizij aktivno, po kratkem zamiku &ktimetracker; bo samodejno "
"začel beležiti čas za to opravilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Idle Detection"
msgstr "Zaznavanje nedejavnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You leave work early on Friday to run an "
"errand and forget to stop the timer. When you return on Monday, the timer is "
"still running."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> V petek zgodaj odidete iz službe po opravku in "
"pozabite ustaviti časovnik. Ko se vrnete v ponedeljek, časovnik še teče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> Turn on idle detection on the "
"<guilabel>Behavior</guilabel> page of the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Vklopite zaznavanje nedejavnosti na strani "
"<guilabel>Vedenje</guilabel> pogovornega okna z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; can be configured to detect when the mouse and keyboard "
"become idle. If the mouse and keyboard are idle for longer than the "
"specified number of minutes, &ktimetracker; displays the following dialog:"
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; lahko konfigurirate tako, da zazna, ko miška in tipkovnica "
"postaneta nedejavni. Če sta miška in tipkovnica nedejavni dlje od podanega "
"števila minut, &ktimetracker; prikaže naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ktimetracker; Idle Detection"
msgstr "&ktimetracker; Zaznavanje nedejavnosti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ktimetracker; Idle Detection Dialog"
msgstr "&ktimetracker; Pogovorno okno za zaznavanje nedejavnosti"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Continue Timing"
msgstr "Nadaljujte z merjenjem časa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply the idle time to all active timers and keep them running."
msgstr "Uporabi čas nedejavnosti za vse aktivne časovnike in pusti, da tečejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You were working on the task(s) while your computer was idle and still are."
msgstr ""
"Delali ste na nalogah, medtem ko je bil vaš računalnik v mirovanju in še "
"vedno ste."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Revert Timing"
msgstr "Povrni čas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subtract the amount of idle time from all active timers and stop them."
msgstr ""
"Od vseh aktivnih časovnikov odštejte čas nedejavnosti in jih zaustavite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You were not working on the task(s) while your computer was idle and you are "
"still not."
msgstr ""
"Niste delali na nalogah, medtem ko je bil vaš računalnik nedejaven, in še "
"vedno ne delate."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Systems"
msgstr "Drugi sistemi"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "&korganizer;"
msgstr "&korganizer;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker;, like &korganizer; and Apple's iCal, uses the industry "
"standard <ulink url=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2445\">iCalendar</"
"ulink> format for its data. &ktimetracker; can read and write the to-do "
"lists created by these two applications."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker;, kot &korganizer; in Applov iCal, za svoje podatke uporablja "
"industrijsko standardno obliko <ulink url=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/"
"rfc2445\">iCalendar</ulink>. &ktimetracker; lahko bere in piše sezname "
"opravil, ki jih ustvarita ti dve aplikaciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can even work synchronously on one file with &korganizer; and "
"&ktimetracker;. If one program changes the file, the updates will be "
"propagated to the other application automatically."
msgstr ""
"Lahko celo sinhrono delate na eni datoteki z &korganizer; in &ktimetracker;. "
"Če en program spremeni datoteko, se posodobitve samodejno prenesejo v drugo "
"aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planner"
msgstr "Planer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As a typical usecase, you might want to plan a project with the project "
"management tool <ulink url=\"&Planner.web;\">&Planner;</ulink> and import "
"its tasks to &ktimetracker; with <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import Tasks From Planner...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, to have them in the industry standard <ulink url="
"\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2445\">iCalendar</ulink> format. Having "
"done so, you are able to schedule the tasks in &korganizer;, and account "
"your time to them in &ktimetracker;. That's one way to help ensure your "
"project stays on time and under budget."
msgstr ""
"Kot tipičen primer uporabe bi morda želeli načrtovati projekt z orodjem za "
"upravljanje projektov <ulink url=\"&Planner.web;\">&Planner;</ulink> in "
"uvoziti njegove naloge v &ktimetracker; z <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvoz</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi opravila iz "
"načrtovalnika...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, da so v industrijskem "
"standardu <ulink url=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2445\">iCalendar</"
"ulink>. Ko to storite, lahko načrtujete naloge v &korganizer; in svoj čas "
"zanje upoštevate v &ktimetracker;. To je eden od načinov, kako zagotoviti, "
"da bo vaš projekt potekal pravočasno in v okviru proračuna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>&DBus;</title>"
msgstr "<title>&DBus;</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; does support numerous methods that can be used with &DBus;."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; podpira številne metode, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti z &DBus;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two ways to use the &DBus; interface: &Qt;'s &GUI; "
"<application>qdbusviewer</application> and the command line "
"<application>qdbus</application>."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva načina za uporabo &DBus; vmesnik: &Qt;'s &GUI; "
"<application>qdbusviewer</application> in ukazna vrstica <application>qdbus</"
"application>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bash script that echoes &ktimetracker;'s version"
msgstr "Bash skript, ki vrne različico &ktimetracker;"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"qdbus org.kde.ktimetracker /KTimeTracker version 2>/dev/null || echo "
"\"ktimetracker not running\""
msgstr ""
"qdbus org.kde.ktimetracker /KTimeTracker različica 2>/dev/null || echo "
"\"ktimetracker ne teče\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker;'s current &DBus; interface is currently used mainly for "
"automated testing, so it is very limited. For the full interface definition, "
"see the <xref linkend=\"dbusappendix\"/>."
msgstr ""
"trenutni &DBus; &ktimetracker; vmesnik se trenutno uporablja predvsem za "
"avtomatsko testiranje, zato je zelo omejen. Za celotno definicijo vmesnika "
"glejte <xref linkend=\"dbusappendix\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see the full &DBus; interface of the &ktimetracker; version installed on "
"your system, run the following Bash script:"
msgstr ""
"Za ogled celotnega &DBus; vmesnik programa &ktimetracker; različico, "
"nameščeno v vašem sistemu, zaženite naslednji skript Bash:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "List &ktimetracker;'s &DBus; interface to console"
msgstr "Seznam &DBus; &ktimetracker; vmesnik do konzole"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"qdbus org.kde.ktimetracker /KTimeTracker 2>/dev/null || echo \"ktimetracker "
"not running\""
msgstr ""
"qdbus org.kde.ktimetracker /KTimeTracker 2>/dev/null || echo \"ktimetracker "
"ne teče\""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export Totals to CSV"
msgstr "Izvozi skupne vrednosti v CSV"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimetracker; can export both totals and history to a comma-delimited file "
"format. To export totals, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Export...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and &ktimetracker; "
"displays the export dialog."
msgstr ""
"&ktimetracker; lahko izvozi vsote in zgodovino v obliko datoteke ločeno z "
"vejicami. Če želite izvoziti vsote, izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvozi...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in "
"&ktimetracker; prikaže pogovorno okno za izvoz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select option <guibutton>Times as CSV</guibutton> in group <guilabel>Report "
"Type</guilabel>. The dialog is going to look as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite možnost <guibutton>Časi kot CSV</guibutton> v skupini "
"<guilabel>Vrsta poročila</guilabel>. Pogovorno okno bo videti takole:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Export Times as CSV</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izvozi čase kot CSV</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Export Times as CSV</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izvozi čase kot CSV</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Modify the dialog defaults if necessary. You can preview the CSV output on "
"the right side of the dialog. Click <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> and "
"&ktimetracker; exports the totals for all tasks to the file you enter in a "
"file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi spremenite privzete nastavitve pogovornega okna. Izpis CSV si "
"lahko ogledate na desni strani pogovornega okna. Kliknite <guibutton>Shrani "
"kot...</guibutton> in &ktimetracker; izvozi vsote za vsa opravila v "
"datoteko, ki jo vnesete v pogovorno okno datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380 index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Copy to Clipboard</guibutton> button to export the times "
"to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Za izvoz časov v odložišče uporabite gumb <guibutton>Kopiraj v odložišče</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is another example of the output format:"
msgstr "Tukaj je še en primer izhodnega formata:"

#. Tag: literallayout
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<computeroutput>\n"
"\"kde\",,,,,0.00,0.00,6.88,9.83\n"
",\"ktimetracker\",,,,6.88,8.70,6.88,9.83\n"
",,\"3.2 feature plan\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",,\"bugs\",,,0.00,1.13,0.00,1.13\n"
",,\"checkin changes - translation strings\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",,\"time card report\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"kopete\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"promo\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"web stuff\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
"</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<computeroutput>\n"
"\"kde\",,,,,0.00,0.00,6.88,9.83\n"
",\"ktimetracker\",,,,6.88,8.70,6.88,9.83\n"
",,\"3.2 feature plan\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",,\"bugs\",,,0.00,1.13,0.00,1.13\n"
",,\"checkin changes - translation strings\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",,\"time card report\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"kopete\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"promo\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"web stuff\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
"</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Top-level tasks are output in the first column, sub-tasks in the second, and "
"so on. The time data is output after the maximum task depth (five in this "
"example). The first time column is <guilabel>Session Time</guilabel>, the "
"second is <guilabel>Time</guilabel>, the third is <guilabel>Total Session "
"Time</guilabel> and the fourth is the <guilabel>Total Time</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Opravila najvišje ravni so izpisane v prvem stolpcu, podopravila v drugem "
"itd. Časovni podatki se izpišejo po največji globini opravila (pet v tem "
"primeru). Prvi časovni stolpec je <guilabel>Čas seje</guilabel>, drugi "
"<guilabel>Čas</guilabel>, tretji <guilabel>Skupni čas seje</guilabel> in "
"četrti <guilabel>Skupni čas </guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export History to CSV"
msgstr "Izvoz zgodovine v CSV"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export task history, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Export...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> and &ktimetracker; displays the same export dialog as shown "
"above. Select option <guibutton>History as CSV</guibutton> in group "
"<guilabel>Report Type</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Za izvoz zgodovine opravil izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Izvoz</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izvoz...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> in &ktimetracker; prikaže isto pogovorno okno za izvoz, kot je "
"prikazano zgoraj. Izberite možnost <guibutton>Zgodovina kot CSV</guibutton> "
"v skupini <guilabel>Vrsta poročila</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a date range that you want the task history to cover. Modify the "
"dialog defaults if necessary. You can preview the CSV output on the right "
"side of the dialog. Click <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> and "
"&ktimetracker; exports the totals for all tasks to the file you enter in a "
"file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberite časovno obdobje, za katerega želite, da zajema zgodovina opravil. "
"Po potrebi spremenite privzete nastavitve pogovornega okna. Izpis CSV si "
"lahko ogledate na desni strani pogovornega okna. Kliknite <guibutton>Shrani "
"kot...</guibutton> in &ktimetracker; izvozi vsote za vsa opravila v "
"datoteko, ki jo vnesete v pogovorno okno datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is an example of the output format:"
msgstr "Tukaj je primer izhodnega formata:"

#. Tag: literallayout
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<computeroutput>\n"
"Task History\n"
"From Tuesday 06 July 2004 to Tuesday 13 July 2004\n"
"Printed on: 2004-07-13 18:10\n"
"2004-07-06,2004-07-07,2004-07-08,2004-07-09,2004-07-10,2004-07-11,2004-07-12,2004-07-13,\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,\"kde\"\n"
",,1.77,3.23,1.73,,1.37,0.82,8.95,,\"ktimetracker\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"3.2 feature plan\"\n"
",1.13,,,,,,,1.13,,,\"bugs\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"checkin changes - translation strings\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"time card report\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"kopete\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"promo\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"web stuff\"\n"
"</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<computeroutput>\n"
"Task History\n"
"From Tuesday 06 July 2004 to Tuesday 13 July 2004\n"
"Printed on: 2004-07-13 18:10\n"
"2004-07-06,2004-07-07,2004-07-08,2004-07-09,2004-07-10,2004-07-11,2004-07-12,2004-07-13,\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,\"kde\"\n"
",,1.77,3.23,1.73,,1.37,0.82,8.95,,\"ktimetracker\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"3.2 feature plan\"\n"
",1.13,,,,,,,1.13,,,\"bugs\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"checkin changes - translation strings\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"time card report\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"kopete\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"promo\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"web stuff\"\n"
"</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first three lines identify when the report was generated and for which "
"date range. The fourth row is a comma-delimited list of the dates in the "
"date range, in ISO 8601 format (YYYY-MM-DD). All subsequent rows list the "
"time logged against each task. The last numeric column is the row total "
"across all days. The task name prints after the total column, and is "
"indented to indicate the task/sub-task relationship. Top level task names "
"appear in the first column after the total."
msgstr ""
"Prve tri vrstice določajo, kdaj je bilo poročilo ustvarjeno in za katero "
"časovno obdobje. Četrta vrstica je z vejicami ločen seznam datumov v "
"časovnem obdobju v formatu ISO 8601 (LLLL-MM-DD). Vse naslednje vrstice "
"navajajo čas, zabeležen za vsako nalogo. Zadnji številski stolpec je vsota "
"vrstic za vse dni. Ime opravila je natisnjeno za stolpcem s skupnim zneskom "
"in je zamaknjeno, da označuje razmerje opravilo/podopravilo. Imena opravil "
"na najvišji ravni so prikazana v prvem stolpcu za skupno vsoto."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &ktimetracker; interface"
msgstr "&ktimetracker; vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main &ktimetracker; window has the following components: menubar, "
"toolbar, searchbar, task/time window and status bar."
msgstr ""
"Glavni &ktimetracker; ima naslednje komponente: menijsko vrstico, orodno "
"vrstico, iskalno vrstico, opravilno/časovno okno in vrstico stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The searchbar is a combined field. As long as you do not press &Enter;, it "
"acts as a filter. Then, only tasks that match your input are shown. As soon "
"as you press &Enter;, your input is used as a name to create a new task."
msgstr ""
"Iskalna vrstica je kombinirano polje. Dokler ne pritisnete &Enter;, deluje "
"kot filter. Nato so prikazana samo opravila, ki se ujemajo z vašim vnosom. "
"Takoj ko pritisnete &Enter;, se vaš vnos uporabi kot ime za ustvarjanje "
"novega opravila.."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Configuration for PDA</guilabel> in the "
"<guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> page of the settings dialog if you have a "
"touchscreen and your screen real estate is precious. It will disable the "
"search bar and every click will pop up a context menu."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Konfiguracija za PDA</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Videz</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami, če imate zaslon "
"na dotik in je površina vašega zaslona dragocena. Onemogočil bo iskalno "
"vrstico in ob vsakem kliku se bo pojavil kontekstni meni."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&ktimetracker; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&ktimetracker; Zaslon</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&ktimetracker; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&ktimetracker; Zaslon</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Task/Time window"
msgstr "Okno Opravila/Čas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The various tasks are displayed in this window, along with the time "
"accumulated for each in the current session and in total. Tasks being timed "
"have a small clock icon next to the session time."
msgstr ""
"V tem oknu so prikazane različna opravila, skupaj s časom, zbranim za vsako "
"v trenutni seji in skupaj. Opravila, ki se časovno določajo, imajo poleg "
"časa seje majhno ikono ure."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Subtasks can be created for each task. Clicking the plus sign and minus sign "
"in front of the main task toggles the view of its associated subtasks. The "
"total time accrued for a task includes the times for its subtasks, as well "
"as its own accumulated time."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako opravilo je mogoče ustvariti podopravila. Če kliknete znak plus in "
"znak minus pred glavnim opravilom, preklopite pogled povezanih podopravil. "
"Skupni čas, zbran za opravilo, vključuje čase za njegova podopravila in "
"lasten skupni čas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Toolbar and Statusbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica in vrstica stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "The toolbar contains icons for the following commands:"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica vsebuje ikone za naslednje ukaze:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "All behave identically to the menu command."
msgstr "Vsi se obnašajo enako kot menijski ukaz."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Task"
msgstr "Novo opravilo"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Subtask"
msgstr "Novo podopravilo"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Začetek"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop"
msgstr "Ustavi"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Uredi"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open"
msgstr "Odpri"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Shrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "The statusbar reports the name of the file where the data was saved."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica stanja poroča o imenu datoteke, v katero so bili shranjeni podatki."

